name: Warmup_Div03_Sub03
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD3S3.CPF,
GmailD3S3.NOME,
GmailD3S3.EMAIL,
GmailD3S3.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S3.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD3S3.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD3S3.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD3S3.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV03_SUB03 GmailD3S3
UNION
